        <p data-uuid="b85513b9d6754902a5419b78db21d73c">Pull factors draw or attract people to another
            location. Countries with good economic opportunities and high salaries are the
            destinations for immigrants attracted to those pull factors. Many immigrants to
            the United States are drawn by economic opportunities. Another example of a
            pull factor is a favorable climate that attracts immigrants to a country.</p>
